<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>썸타임에 오신 것을 환영합니다!</title>
    <style>
        /* 전체 스타일 */
        body {
            font-family: 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Noto Sans KR', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* 컨테이너 스타일 */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        /* 헤더 스타일 */
        .header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 180px;
            height: auto;
        }

        /* 콘텐츠 스타일 */
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555555;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* 버튼 스타일 */
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #FF6B6B;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #FF5252;
        }

        /* 정보 섹션 스타일 */
        .info-section {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .info-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            width: 120px;
            color: #666666;
        }

        .info-value {
            color: #333333;
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* 푸터 스타일 */
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999999;
            border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .social-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #666666;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .social-link:hover {
            color: #FF6B6B;
        }

        .footer-text {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        /* 반응형 스타일 */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .info-item {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .info-label {
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://sometimes-resources.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/resources/sometime-logo.png"
                alt="썸타임 로고" class="logo">
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">안녕하세요, {{name}}님!</div>

            <div class="message">
                <p>썸타임에 가입해주셔서 진심으로 감사합니다. 대학생 매칭 서비스 썸타임과 함께 새로운 인연을 만나보세요.</p>
                <p>지금 바로 프로필을 완성하고 매칭을 시작해보세요!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">프로필 완성하기</a>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="info-title">가입 정보</div>

                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">이름</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{name}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">이메일</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{email}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">대학교</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{university}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">가입일</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{signupDate}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://instagram.com/sometime" class="social-link">Instagram</a>
                <a href="https://facebook.com/sometime" class="social-link">Facebook</a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/sometime" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-text">
                본 메일은 발신 전용으로 회신이 불가합니다.
            </div>

            <div class="footer-text">
                &copy; 2025 썸타임. All rights reserved.
            </div>

            <div class="footer-text">
                <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}" style="color: #999999; text-decoration: underline;">수신 거부</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>